    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a showroom-quality shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine runs exceptionally smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a driving experience that feels brand new. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in impeccable, top-tier condition with a complete service history.",
