    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 Audi Q5 has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The Moonlight Blue Metallic exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the Nougat Brown leather seats are supple and free of any cracks, tears, or stains, and the vehicle has been kept strictly smoke-free. All technological features, including the Virtual Cockpit and the panoramic sunroof, function perfectly. Mechanically, this SUV is robust and ready for the road. It comes with a complete service history documenting regular maintenance intervals, and we recently performed a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection. The tires offer excellent tread depth, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system delivers a smooth, planted ride. This is a reliable, sophisticated vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and daily practicality.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
